filters
| essql 
  query="SELECT \"Running instances\"  FROM \"filebeat-*\" ORDER BY \"@timestamp\" DESC LIMIT 1"
| mapColumn "Running instances" exp={getCell "Running instances" | if {compare "gte" to=50}  then=1 else= 0 }
| getCell "Running instances"
| revealImage origin="bottom" image={asset "asset-957fc466-e55a-49a1-914a-defb89a77d66"} emptyImage={asset "asset-577751e4-576a-4baa-8efb-c9fb494ae974"}
| render

filters
